channel.title: CVE Feed for IBM -- i2 Analyst Notebook
channel.description: The latest CVEs for IBM -- i2 Analyst Notebook

item.title: CVE-2020-4554|2024-08-04T08:07:48.918Z -- ibm -- i2%20analyst%20notebook
item.description: IBM i2 Analyst Notebook 9.2.1 and 9.2.2 could allow a local attacker to execute arbitrary code on the system, caused by a memory corruption. By persuading a victim to open a specially-crafted file, an attacker could exploit this vulnerability to execute arbitrary code on the system. IBM X-Force ID: 183322.
